             Ted's New Adventures Version 1.0
Editor Commands
KEY         GADGET         AMIGA +        ACTION
Q           Double Box     Q              Quit Boulderdash
P           Joystick       P              Play a Game
T           T-Symbol       T              Test current game field
Left        Arrow Left     -              Move Field One Place Left
Right       Arrow Right    -              Move Field One Place Right
Up          Arrow Up       -              Move Field One Place Up
Down        Arrow Down     -              Move Field One Place Down
-           D Arrow Left   -              Move to the Left of Field
-           D Arrow Right  -              Move to the Right of Field
-           D Arrow Up     -              Move to the Top of Field
-           D Arrow Down   -              Move to the Bottom of Field
-           Disk+Arrow R   W              Save Field to Disk
-           Disk+Arrow L   O              Load Field From Disk
help        Question Mark  H              This Message
-           Watch          I              Set Game Time
-           Three Digits   A              Set Game Target

While Playing Press ESC to Quit the Game.  Have Fun...
